ad takes inspiration from several sources to provide a rich
"integrating development environment" experience.

    - https://research.swtch.com/acme

    - above is a link to Russ Cox's "A tour of acme" video.
      it is a fantastic introduction to the power and flexability you can
      achieve through pursuing the idea of a "text user interface".

    - you can learn more about acme here: http://acme.cat-v.org/

    - ad combines acme's approach to manipulating text, with modal editing
      inspired by vi and kakoune:
        - https://www.vim.org/
        - https://neovim.io/
        - https://kakoune.org/

    - it also embeds a dynamic selection menu inspired by dmenu:
        - https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu/
